title: Oh My
lyrics:
You say I'm obsessive..
I don't want to hear
Overly posessive..
Who, when, and where?
When your arms go around another..
Well I'll turn my back why bother? (yeah)

-

Forget the importance

Of what I mean to you

I'll drown all the rodents

And chase after you

Well I've made my mistakes and know it

And I need a chance to blow it

-

(chorus)

Oh oh my!

Who's stolen my right? (yeah)

-

Am I gettin' greedy..

..for what's already mine?

I need all the rations

I don't stand in line

And I'll scale the wall

Only if you feed the rope

But I'll slip and fall



-

(chorus)

Oh oh my!

Who'll ever believe and why?

-

Oh oh my!

I'm the last in line..

-

You say I'm obsessive..

I don't want to hear

Overly posessive..
